"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"952c82",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Present in the outstretched arm position and with various actions; commonly (but not universally) associated with a positive family history and improvement with alcohol; possible presence of head and voice tremor; possible emergence (after a delay of several seconds) of a postural tremor of the outstretched arms"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
