},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"e63408",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Enhanced physiologic tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"fd7946",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Noticeable form of physiologic low-amplitude, high-frequency tremor seen in association with triggers, such as stress, caffeine, drugs, and thyroid disease; similar to essential tremor but resolves with resolution of underlying trigger"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
