"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[

]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"9a18e3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Fragile X-associated tremor/ataxia syndrome"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"3b06d3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Neurodegenerative disease seen in older men who are carriers of a premutation in the fragile X intellectual disability 1 gene; typically, there is a family history of intellectual disability in young males and premature ovarian failure in females; symptoms of (intention) tremor, ataxia, parkinsonism, neuropathy and dementia"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-2 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"d86656",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Rubral tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"59c66d",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Cerebellar outflow disorders (multiple sclerosis, stroke, traumatic brain injury)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"41ee4b",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Coarse proximal tremor present at rest, worse with posturing (especially large-amplitude and proximal tremors in the wing-beating position with elbows flexed), and most severe during movements"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-2 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"74396e",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Task-specific tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"486e3a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Primary writing tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f61452",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Only present with specific task"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
