"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ed72c3",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Orthostatic tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ed72c3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Orthostatic tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"769d99",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"High-frequency tremor emerging in the legs only during standing (orthostatic position) and resolving with sitting or walking"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-2 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"4bc573",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Neuropathic tremor"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"1cb480",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Demyelinating neuropathies"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ff8caa",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Action tremor, associated with weakness, areflexia, and sensory loss"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
}
]
}
]
},
"footnotes":[
[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sup",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"a"
]
},
"Tremor present with the affected extremity resting unsupported."
],
[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sup",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"b"
]
},
"Postural tremor is present with the arm in an outstretched position, and kinetic tremor is present during reaching, writing, and other movements."
],
[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sup",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"c"
]
},
"Intention tremor is a specific subtype of kinetic tremor that becomes very prominent near target, exhibiting a crescendo of increased severity at the terminal section of the movement path."
]
]
}